init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You watch as you slowly become an adult, get married, have kids and experience all the highs and lows of life.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You look at the people around you who are also experiencing that wave, and then you realize that it has been happening every time someone in your previous life

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You then realize that you have never truly lived life to the fullest and you want to change that.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You turn to the man sitting next to you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The man raises a hand and smiles.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: And the ending wasn't an ending at all.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Main Character would have to spice it up a little bit.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It was a happy ending, but it needed more.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She wrote a note on the paper.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She wanted to end it all with a bang.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Main Character sat down in her reclining chair and watched the New Film.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The New Film was a masterpiece.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The audience stood up and applauded.
